column3: Which professional surfers were born on the Philippines?
column4: "which surfers were born in Philippines?"
column9:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {
	?uri dbo:occupation res:Surfing .
	?uri dbo:birthPlace res:Philippines .
}
